was celebrated or will celebrate, they can use this system and get the day within a second. The system works based on Ethipian calender.
Oh....that's awesome: Right now you can know in which day Ethiopian new year will celebrate after 1000 years or before 1000 years ago. Really? It's unbelievable. But in Day_Finder you can! Come on!
